{"tid":2442681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：據世衞定義「疫苗接種異常事件」是指事件發生在接種後 其因果關為不確定","createTime":"2021-03-11T13:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T13:46:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf8838b14ea68f058394bf4f4942129e1846208","tid":2442681,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"衞生署接獲兩宗懷疑與接種新冠疫苗後出現嚴重的異常事件報告<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  衞生署今日（三月十一日）公布，截至今日下午四時的過去24小時，衞生署接獲醫院管理局（醫管局）呈報一宗死亡及一宗危殆個案的呈報，懷疑涉及與接種新冠疫苗後出現嚴重異常事件的報告。<br />\n<br />\n  根據醫管局提供的資料，第一宗個案涉及一名70歲女子，本身患有高血壓及退化性膝關節炎。她今天早上出現氣喘，中午在家中暈倒，送往廣華醫院搶救無效，於今日下午證實死亡。根據死者家屬提供的資料，她曾於三月二日在九龍灣體育館社區疫苗接種中心接種科興新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n  第二宗個案涉及一名67歲男子，本身患有糖尿病、高血壓及高血脂症。他今日中午突然在旺角地鐵站暈倒，被送往廣華醫院。初步診斷是急性冠狀動脈綜合症，現時情況危殆。根據資料，他曾於三月二日在私家診所接種科興新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n  衞生署接獲呈報後已即時聯絡醫管局，就事件獲取更多資料以進行調查及評估。根據世界衞生組織，疫苗接種異常事件是指免疫接種後發生的、不一定與疫苗使用有因果關係的任何不幸的醫療事件。衞生署會在取得所有相關資料（包括第一宗個案的初步解剖報告）後，盡快交由新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會按世界衞生組織的算法流程，進行因果關係評估。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2021年3月11日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間20時25分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202103/11/P2021031100727.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202103%2F11%2FP2021031100727.htm&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=6f1fd1df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202103/11/P2021031100727.htm</a>"},{"pid":"53fa6d4dafe68e2eb7ae6ab9e48803ce62ea9b3d","tid":2442681,"uid":165136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"definition 放最後嗰段<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新聞處啲友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eea1af0c973b667bd109edf91bf8138ddda1563","tid":2442681,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"市民話唔打針 港共就話講呢番說話嘅人搞搞震<br />\n<br />\n科興針打死人 港共出新稿嗰個人有併發症糖尿病<br />\n<br />\n港共政府雙重標準到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d239c6eecb3e750909640ab3169e03f7d30bb28","tid":2442681,"uid":52876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"無野搵野黎講? 有退化性膝關節炎都要提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f9c5a1e88eabefe85d66fd8c60d66de430bc93","tid":2442681,"uid":95577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"得喇得喇<br />\n總之同疫苗無關係啦<br />\n寫咁長想呃稿費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd04a51bc91da225861ce75662926fbaed86df4","tid":2442681,"uid":31620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:39:33.000Z","msg":"消滅低端人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目的為了讓周邊地區的就業人口獲益，並維持香港特別行政區的產能平衡、保障良好環境與社會秩序等。"},{"pid":"f2c707bad1fd346981f41ab78a9c7be333542f2e","tid":2442681,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"其實係咪即係要一打完枝針即場瓜先有得賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da940546213e33e6a112a0fbb70a560c1e6687db","tid":2442681,"uid":135169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"世衛：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPnKwgy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPnKwgy.jpg&h=4832cb3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f544872c563f442eeae33a54df880b8741e2f4c","tid":2442681,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:41:41.000Z","msg":"咁世衛有冇講 冇食早餐打疫苗會死？而咁樣死係唔關疫苗事？"},{"pid":"a358bedfb7e51959a19d0f9eeef316542bbfa8a2","tid":2442681,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zh3JMRB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZh3JMRB.gif&h=96a8a84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又要貼由高登到連登咁耐以來我最鍾意嘅gif圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}